title: Delivery of the YP Real Yellow Pages(SM) Residential White Pages Listings to Change in Kentucky
text:
Submitted by admin on 9/11/2015 @ 12:17 PM Companies mentioned in this article: Print Media 
CORBIN, Ky., Sept. 11, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- Print Media LLC, publisher and distributor of the YP Real Yellow Pages(SM) directory, announced today that residential white pages listings (provided by AT&T) will no longer be included in YP Real Yellow Pages(SM) directories in select markets across Kentucky, including the city of Corbin. 
As the official white pages publisher for AT&T, Print Media offers a variety of choices for accessing the free residential white pages listings including: -- Using www.RealPagesLive.com, which includes the YP Real Yellow Pages? directory with residential white pages, business white pages, and government pages listings. -- Ordering a free version of the residential white pages listings directory on CD-ROM or in print by calling 1-866-329-7118 or going to www.mydirectories.yp.com. -- Accessing and searching residential listings on YP.com - among the 40 most visited web properties in the U.S. 
About Print Media 
Print Media publishes and distributes the YP Real Yellow Pages? directory that consumers use to find quality products and services in their area. Working every day with YP, our corporate partner, Print Media offers advertising solutions proven to help businesses grow. Print Media is owned by affiliates of Cerberus Capital Management and AT&T.
